<br>
Finally managed to get my hands on 2 MP Hand Axes (yeah, you know im the axe freak). Damn, I was so happy... the poor smith had to work hard on thosem with lots of salvages.<br>
<br>
My problem here is that Mythic pushes me into the Jambiyas always... better DPS/Speed, allowed to use it to the fullest at R5, but above all, MP Jambs have 32 points to spend in Spellcrafting, while MP Hand Axes have 29.<br>
<br>
Mythic keeps pushing me as a mercenary, if I want to do the most damage, with the best SC template, onto the type of weapons I dont wanna see myself with (and yes, I have 2 set of Jambiyas in my vault).<br>
<br>
Where is the diversity, seing people with different weapon setups ? Every damn slash mercenary I see is wearing Jambiyas or Jambiyas/Sabre. Some may do it for the looks, but others do it PLAIN and SIMPLY for they are the best at &quot;level 51&quot; and at Spellcrafting them.<br>
<br>
Will I give up my hand axes ? Never... but I am very disgusted at Mythic <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START >: --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/mad.gif ALT=">:"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
