I truly do dislike the look of PCrafted weaponry though.<br>
<br>
Slash weapons- what you would use if you were Lawrence of Arabia. ONLY EXCEPTION- the Polearm. It could be worse. <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong> It could be called the Ceremonial Naginatana </strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->. Wait, actually that would be cool! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <br>
