Crush weapons- sort of plain and very square. They look nice and heavy though, like they could REALLY crush stuff.<br>
<br>
Thrust weapons- something you stole from a display case, from the mansion of the Count of Monte Cristo.<br>
<br>
Where's the individuality? Hell, I still want to see Crush and Slash infiltrators! <br>
